  "keyFeatures": [
    "Volo.Abp.Core foundation (AbpApplicationBase, modularity, DI, virtual file system)",
    "Modularity system with AbpModule and dependency graph",
    "Dependency Injection extensions and conventional registration",
    "Dynamic proxy / interception aspects (Castle integration)",
    "Domain-Driven Design layer (Domain.Shared, Domain, Application.Contracts, Application)",
    "Entities, aggregate roots, value objects, repositories, domain services, specifications",
    "Unit of Work with ambient context and event ordering",
    "Data layer: connection strings, data filtering, data seeding, migrations",
    "Entity Framework Core integration with SQL Server, PostgreSQL, MySQL, SQLite, Oracle providers",
    "MongoDB, Dapper, MemoryDb persistence providers",
    "ASP.NET Core integration: MVC, Razor Pages, SignalR, Serilog, Swashbuckle",
    "MVC UI: Bootstrap theme, bundling, widgets, dynamic JS proxies",
    "Authentication: JWT Bearer, OAuth, OpenID Connect, IdentityModel",
    "Authorization framework and Permission system",
    "Multi-Tenancy with tenant resolvers and connection string resolver",
    "Local and distributed Event Bus (RabbitMQ, Kafka, Azure Service Bus, Dapr, Rebus)",
    "Background Jobs and Background Workers (Hangfire, Quartz, RabbitMQ, TickerQ)",
    "Distributed Locking (with Dapr provider)",
    "Caching (in-memory + StackExchange Redis distributed cache)",
    "BLOB Storing providers (Azure, AWS S3, Google Cloud, Aliyun, Bunny, MinIO, FileSystem, Memory)",
    "Auditing and AuditLogging module",
    "Validation (DataAnnotations + FluentValidation)",
    "Features and GlobalFeatures",
    "Settings and SettingManagement module",
    "Localization (resources, abstractions, multi-lingual objects)",
    "Text Templating (Razor, Scriban)",
    "Imaging (ImageSharp, SkiaSharp, MagickNet)",
    "Emailing (MailKit) and SMS (Aliyun, Tencent Cloud)",
    "HTTP client + Remote Services (IdentityModel auth flows for MVC/Blazor/MAUI)",
    "AI abstractions",
    "Dapr integration (sidecar event bus, distributed lock, HTTP client, MVC)",
    "Autofac and AutoMapper / Mapperly object mapping",
    "Blazor UI stack (Server, WebAssembly, Web App, MauiBlazor, BlazoriseUI)",
    "MAUI client integration",
    "UI Navigation menu system",
    "Minification",
    "Application modules: Identity, Account, OpenIddict, IdentityServer, PermissionManagement, SettingManagement, FeatureManagement, TenantManagement, AuditLogging, BackgroundJobs, BlobStoring.Database, CmsKit, Blogging, Docs, Users, VirtualFileExplorer, BasicTheme, ClientSimulation",
    "Angular UI packages (ng-packs): core, account, identity, permission-management, setting-management, feature-management, tenant-management, cms-kit, components, oauth, schematics, generators, theme-basic, theme-shared",
    "ABP CLI command set (new, add-module, install-libs, generate-proxy, bundle, build, switch-to-*, login, translate, mcp)",
    "Cli.Core: ProjectBuilding, ProjectModification, ServiceProxying, Licensing, GitHub, Bundling",
    "Solution templates (app, app-nolayers, module, console, maui, wpf) with Angular and ASP.NET Core variants",
    "Test base infrastructure (Volo.Abp.TestBase, AspNetCore.TestBase)",
    "Build scripts (PowerShell), deploy/NuGet/NPM publish scripts",
    "AI rules folder for ABP coding conventions",
    "GDPR abstractions",
    "Object extending system"
  ],
